headline: Telsey Advisory Maintains Market Perform Rating on Dollar Tree (DLTR), Lifts PT
summary: On May 27, Telsey Advisory Group analyst Joseph Feldman upped the price target on Dollar Tree, Inc. (NASDAQ:DLTR)’s stock to $95.00 from $82.00, while maintaining a “Market Perform” rating. headline: 3 S&P 500 Stocks Facing Headwinds
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
